The app EX051.07 Dual Unit of Measure for Close Documents extends the features of app [EX041 Close Documents Without Invoicing]({{<relref "close-documents-without-invoicing">}}) and allows closing document lines with a secondary unit of measure.

The feature allows to specify the secondary quantity on the journal; the secondary quantity is also automatically suggested according to what was actually shipped or received.

