Example of Close Document Entries:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000957-0/CDW2_ENU.png"><br>

**Please note**
Closing the secondary quantity without closing the main quantity is not allowed:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000957-0/CDW3_ENU.png"><br>


